Module FloWeekTracker

module FloWeekTracker

This module provides packages required for the FloWeek Tracker application.


FloWeekTracker description

FloWeekTracker is an application in Polish language designed to improve weekly productivity. This application has two parts:

  • Task Names: Contains and manages unique task names which are used during task creation. Users can:
    • add or remove task name,
    • check the task names list
  • Planner: Allows creating a personal weekly calendar, where each task includes a task name, description, time, weekday, and done status. Users can:
    • add, edit or remove a task in the planner,
    • check the daily plan for each day of the week,
    • mark tasks as done,
    • check the total points earned for each day as well as the points to achieve.

FloWeekTracker is designed to help users organize their weekly tasks efficiently, offering tools to plan, track, and evaluate their productivity.
